items.title: Barbie Rapunzel
items.brief:
Rapunzel - Long long ago, and a time of magic and dragons, there lived a young maiden name Rapunzel who had beautiful, long flowing hair. And trapped and the enchanted tower, Rapunzel escapes in Time to save two kingdoms. Barbie as Rapunzel and Pennelope doll - Relive the beauty with Barbie dolls fairy tale collection!

Doll is brand new in box... Excellent condition. Never opened or removed from box and has been stored in a smoke free environment.

items.title: Barbie Matinee Today
items.brief: Gift your little one the ‘Matinee Today Barbie’ doll by Mattel, and see a lovely smile light up her face. This 1996 Barbie sports a beautiful, short pink jacket and skirt, making her very attractive. The black colored hand bag along with the stocking and matching pumps of the ‘Matinee Today Barbie’ give her a stylish and elegant look. The black and white punk hairstyle of this doll by Mattel enhances her appeal. With well-matched accessories, this doe eyed 1996 Barbie is sure to keep your child entertained for days if not months.
